title: Party Rockets GT
text:
Party Rockets GT (Japanese: Party Rockets GT, Hepburn: Pātīrokettsu Jītī) was a Japanese idol girl group formed in 2012. They participated in the 2015 Tokyo Idol Festival. Their single "Let’s Go!!" reached the 15th place on the Weekly Oricon Singles Chart.
They disbanded after their final tour on February 24, 2020.
